	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>O.K. I have a level 24 bard on tallon zek (pvp)&nbsp;&nbsp;I am constantly getting my A** handed to me by pkers.  I can run, but that's no fun and I hate getting taunted across the zone while doing it.<br>I have read a lot of posts about bards being great, but i haven't been able to see it yet.  What am I doing wrong.  What is the strategy with the bard?  When I fight casters, they root and nuke from a distance, when i fight mele I have to run because they are dealing so much more damage than I am.  Please help<br>Thanks<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
