	   <tr><td colspan=2>I play a 51 bard and have found a tactic that works very well, on mobs that would otherwise be too tough. This will work for a two people or a full group. <br><br>It is a very easy concept, Live Bait. The bard is used for live bait. Find a lone mob, hit him with snare, chant of flame, and chant of frost. Kite him for just a few rounds of your songs, then have your partner or group come in behind him and start swinging. The songs make the mob so mad that it will almost never turn on the other players. I have used this to kill white and yellow mobs, with only a rogue for a partner. Oh and dont even try it with casters :)<br><br>Olanya Taban<br>Bard 51st level<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
